	<!--ChiYou Halberd-->
	<ThingDef Class="RI_Starch.RI_ThingDef.RI_DragonPatternStick" ParentName="RI_MagicalWeapon_Sharp_Base">
		<defName>RI_Weapon_ChiYouFlameHalberd</defName>
		<label>ChiYou flame halberd【First-rate】</label>
		<description>【First-rate】Melee weapon\n\nA long halberd with violent power, the whole body constantly spewing fire. The halberd is said to have been inspired by the ancient myth of Chiyou, the warrior master, whose anger still burns bright and gushes out through the halberd.</description>
